'''麥克·肖爾戴斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Mark Shouldice'''}}，{{bd|1977年|12月21日||}}），又被稱為'''麥克·戴斯'''（'''Mark Dice'''），是一名美國YouTube名人、陰謀論者和作家，知名於有關[[秘密組織|秘密組織]]的[[陰謀論|陰謀論]]，例如[[光明會|光明會]]、[[畢德堡俱樂部|畢德堡俱樂部]]、[[骷髏會|骷髏會]]、{{link-en|Bohemian Grove|Bohemian Grove}}和[[撒旦崇拜|撒旦崇拜]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.markdice.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=119&Itemid=95 |title = Mark Dice Bio |publisher = MarkDice.com |language = en |accessdate = 2016-05-24 |archive-date = 2016-06-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160623183431/http://markdice.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=119&Itemid=95 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 生涯 ==
2005年，戴斯寫了一本關於光明會及[[新世界秩序|新世界秩序]]陰謀論的書籍《''The Resistance Manifesto''》，很快地在互聯網的陰謀群組中受到大眾歡迎。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.prisonplanet.com/articles/december2006/131206_b_Bonaduce.htm |title = Danny Bonaduce meets John Conner |date = 2006-12-13 |publisher = PRISON PLANET.com |language = en |access-date = 2006-12-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20061218202100/http://www.prisonplanet.com/articles/december2006/131206_b_Bonaduce.htm |archive-date = 2006-12-18 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>2009年，他出版《''The Illuminati: Facts & Fiction''》，主要討論有關光明會的可能性。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://newsok.com/book-aims-to-shed-light-on-illuminati/article/3367762 |title = Book "Angels and Demons" aims to shed light on Illuminati |author = Carla Hinton |date = 2009-05-09 |publisher = NewsOK |language = en |accessdate = 2016-05-24 |archive-date = 2012-12-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121230113142/http://newsok.com/book-aims-to-shed-light-on-illuminati/article/3367762 |dead-url = no }}</ref>他也持續寫有關秘密組織、陰謀論和政府監控問題的書。

